{
  "info": {
    "name": "D2 Ride Booking - IAM Admin APIs",
    "description": "Admin IAM CRUD + role/permission assignment endpoints. Requires Cognito JWT with ADMIN system group.\n\n**Authentication Setup:**\n1. Get Cognito JWT token (use AWS Cognito SDK or hosted UI)\n2. Set the `COGNITO_JWT` collection variable to your token\n3. Token must have `cognito:groups` claim including `admin`\n\n**Required Permissions:**\n- Endpoints enforce permission-based RBAC\n- User must have granted permissions via role assignments in DB\n- See endpoint descriptions for required permission keys",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "BASE_URL",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "COGNITO_JWT",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{COGNITO_JWT}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
